cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category as the paper deals with medical image classification and localization using deep learning techniques. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel deep learning architecture for multi-class classification and localization. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses deep learning techniques for automated detection of abnormalities in medical imaging. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with medical imaging and mammograms. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the incorporation of local annotations into the model for improved performance measures.
